$I_L\uparrow$.
\[ R_L \uparrow \Longrightarrow V \uparrow \Longrightarrow V/R_0 \uparrow
	\Longrightarrow I_L \downarrow \]

\htmladdimg{../figures/currentsource.gif}

The slope of the voltage-current curve is the internal resistance:
\[	R_0=\frac{\triangle V}{\triangle I}	\]

